                            <div class="modal-body">
                                <!-- Project Details Go Here -->
                                <h2>Fighter Project</h2>
								<br>	
								<div class="img-responsive img-centered"> <!-- class="preview" align="center"> -->
									<img name="preview4" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/q1.jpg" alt=""/>
								</div>
								<div class="thumbnails" align ="center">
									<img onmouseover="preview4.src=img13.src" name="img13" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/q1.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview4.src=img14.src" name="img14" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/q2.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview4.src=img15.src" name="img15" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/q3.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview4.src=img16.src" name="img16" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/q4.jpg" alt=""/>
								</div>
								<h3>Role:</h3>
								<p>I designed and developed this project using the Unreal Engine. I also made all of the animations using recorded video reference. It is a 2 player fighter game. The goal of the game is to get the other player's health to 0 before they get yours to 0. The first player to win 3 fights, wins the game.</p>
								<br>
								<div class="imagespacing"><embed width="640" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UiGGbjNTpLs" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></div>
								<br>
								<h3>How to Play:</h3>
								<p>Player 1: Use 'A' and 'D' to move left and right. 'Q' to Jab, 'W' to Hook, 'E' to Uppercut, and 'R' to block.
Player 2: Use 'J' and 'L' to move left and right. 'U' to Jab, 'I' to Hook, 'O' to Uppercut, and 'P' to block.
								</p>
                                <ul class="list-inline">
                                    <li>Date: August 2015</li>
                                    <li>Software: Unreal Engine 4</li>
                                    <li>Category: Games</li>
                                </ul>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i> Close Project</button>
                            </div>
