                                <!-- Project Details Go Here -->
                                <h2>Jupiter Jones</h2>
								<br>	
								<div class="img-responsive img-centered"> <!-- class="preview" align="center"> -->
									<img name="preview5" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/j4.jpg" alt=""/>
								</div>
								<div class="thumbnails" align ="center">
									<img onmouseover="preview5.src=img17.src" name="img17" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/j1.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview5.src=img18.src" name="img18" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/j2.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview5.src=img19.src" name="img19" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/j3.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview5.src=img20.src" name="img20" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/j4.jpg" alt=""/>
								</div>
								<h3>Role:</h3>
								<p>This project went through many iterations with different team members. My main contributions to this project were through game design, level design, and environmental art. I worked with my teammates to decide on theme and direction for the project and then designed levels that would function well with our game mechanics. As an environmental artist I used assets from the Unity store and the textures were found online. The project was build using Unity 3D.
								</p>
								<br>
								<div class="imagespacing"><embed width="640" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KxweJuUBPHI" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></div>
								<br>
								<h3>How to Play:</h3>
								<p>Use 'W', 'A', 'S', 'D' (WASD) to move the player and spacebar to jump. The mouse is used to look around. The left mouse click pushes yellow blocks away from you and will push you away from red blocks. The right mouse click pulls yellow blocks towards you and pulls you towards red blocks. You can also pick up yellow blocks by holding down the right mouse button. Navigate the temple to find the lost emerald.</p>
                                <h3>Overview:</h3>
								<p>Jupiter Jones is an adventure game that follows a space aged adventurer. Using his industrial space construction gun, Jupiter navigates an ancient alien temple on the moon of Titan searching for lost treasure. He must face many puzzles in challenges in his search for glory!</p>
								<ul class="list-inline">
                                    <li>Date: April 2016</li>
                                    <li>Software: Unity</li>
                                    <li>Category: Games</li>
                                </ul>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i> Close Project</button>
