                                <h2>Gloom Box</h2>
								<br>	
								<div class="img-responsive img-centered">
									<img name="preview7" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/gloom2.jpg" alt=""/>
								</div>
								<div class="thumbnails" align ="center">
									<img onmouseover="preview7.src=img25.src" name="img25" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/gloom1.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview7.src=img26.src" name="img26" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/gloom2.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview7.src=img27.src" name="img27" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/gloom3.jpg" alt=""/>
									<img onmouseover="preview7.src=img28.src" name="img28" src="img/portfolio/fullsize/gloom4.jpg" alt=""/>
								</div>
								<h3>Role:</h3>
								<p>I have multiple roles for Gloom Box including: Game Design, UI Design, UX Design, Visual Coordinator, and Sound Editing. I worked on this project with a team of 4 other students over the course of 2 semesters. The project will function as my Master's Capstone for my degree in Game Design and Development at the Rochester Institute of Technology.</p> 
								<br><br>
								<div class="imagespacing"><embed width="640" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4OMEZwioaJg" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></div>
								<br>
								<h3>Description:</h3>
								<p>Gloom Box is a music themed 2D puzzle/platformer game. Follow Muse as she explores the world of Opus with her boombox companion, Gloom. Use music to alter the world and solve puzzles. Mash up music to discover new abilities.</p>
