                                <h2>ONMYOJI (阴阳师)</h2>
								<br>	
								<div class="imagespacing"><embed width="640" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0DdkOykOpAo" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></div>
								<h3>Role:</h3>
								<p>I worked as a UI designer on this game as part of my internship at NetEase Games. As part of the game design team, I was given different design issues for 阴阳师 and asked to complete research and prototypes as to how the problems could be fixed. My first assignment was to try to make the monster summoning process more meaningful to the player. My final prototype with research/documentation can be downloaded or viewed below. I also was asked to create a VR demo for the battle system in 阴阳师. The results of this project can be viewed in this portfolio under "Pokemon Battle".</p>
								<p><a class="links" href="http://yys.163.com/" target="_blank">Download Game Here</a></p>
								<br>
								<h3>Description:</h3>
								<p>As of December 2016 it is the highest grossing mobile game on the Chinese iOS store and 6th globally. 阴阳师 follows a Yin Yang master and his friends as they interact and battle with monsters from Japanese mythology. The game can be downloaded and played on iOS and Android.</p> 
								<div class="imagespacing"><embed width="640" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kPrkTdDQyIw" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></div>
