                                <h2>Pokemon Battle</h2>
								<br>	
								<div class="imagespacing"><embed width="640" height="480" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MBuWtsywUM0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></div>
								<br>
								<h3>Role:</h3> 
								<p>This is a demo I created as part of my internship at NetEase games. I created all parts of this project using the Google VR API and art assets that I found online. The goal was to create a VR prototype for the game, 阴阳师 using Google VR. My assignment was to focus on the games battle system. This battle system can be applied to many turn based RPG's. I chose Pokemon as a placeholder. The Pokemon models were downloaded from a free 3D model website.</p>
								<p>The project in its entirety can be downloaded below. This includes the Unity project, VR Setup & Research Report, and .apk build for Android devices. The .apk file can be played on any android device but it is recommended to be used with Google Cardboard.</p>
                                <p><a class="links" href="https://www.dropbox.com/home/Portfolio/Pokemon%20Battle%20VR" target="_blank">Download Project Here</a></p>
